  <acronym>APCORD</acronym>
  <official_title>A Prospective Phase II Study to Evaluate Cord Blood Transplantation in Inherited or Acquired Severe Aplastic Anemia Refractory or in Relapse After Immunosuppressive Therapy</official_title>
