    <intervention_name>Cord Blood Transplantation</intervention_name>
    <description>One or 2 cord blood units containing alone or both together more than 4x107 frozen nucleated cells/Kg with no more than 2 out of 6 HLA mismatches between them and with the patients for acquired Severe Aplastic Anemia</description>
